      "id": "d6471592b64746e5",
      "text": "In the 13th chapter I will then show how we succeed in earthly self-localization thanks to the help of the sky and what consequences it has for our self-understanding and relationship to the world that we can have orientation services immediately available everywhere: *Everywhere like at home: Global Positioning System*."
